##Updating Feature Image

Follow the instructions to update a feature image.

**NOTE: ** the resolution of the image should be `780px Wide` by `430px High`

1. Click **Remove featured image**

    ![]({{ images }}Feature-Remove-Image.png)

2. Click **Set Featured Image**

    ![]({{ images }}Feature-Add-New-Image.png)

3. Upload load and choose image as you normally would. 

4. Click **Upload Featured Image** button

5. Click the update button and your done!